OOC: What is he looking for already?

BIC:

Ragnar, Roger Sir. I will contact back once I make contact. Bear Alpha 
out.

He picked up speed, walking faster and faster and shaking the ground 
more as he went on. From the progress he was making on his 
positionning screen and the various readouts his instruments gave him, 
he estimated he would get there in about an hour.
